sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant LoginPage as Login Page
    participant AuthServer as Auth Server
    participant Dashboard

    User->>LoginPage: Enter username & password
    LoginPage->>AuthServer: Send credentials
    AuthServer-->>LoginPage: Validate credentials (success/failure)
    LoginPage-->>User: Show error or redirect
    LoginPage->>Dashboard: Redirect on success
    Dashboard-->>User: Display user dashboard